cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

The paper proposes a deep learning technique for myocardial segmentation in cardiac MRI, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves medical imaging (cs.MM) as it deals with the analysis of MRI scans for cardiac function.
